    • Method Detail

      • getAlias

        public java.lang.String getAlias(Expression e)
        Get the "default" name for a given expression. Used to assign variable names to the schema of a computed select statement. At the moment, only Columns get special names: SELECT A FROM ... is equivalent to SELECT A AS A FROM ...

      • getAlias

        public java.lang.String getAlias(Expression e,
                                 java.util.List otherSelectItems)
        Get the default name for a given expression in a way guaranteed not to collide with other expressions in a specified list. Names are assigned using the default name if possible, and then by appending 0, 1, 2, ...

        public PlanNode getPlan()
                 throws java.sql.SQLException
